The best way to protect yourself is to get vaccinated and boosted when recommended. 

Continue wearing masks – especially in crowded indoor spaces. 

And for the indoors, keep the air fresh by opening windows and doors, and invest in good ventilation.

#COVID19 is not over yet. https://t.co/GiGOWGDWCz
